      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZAP DEVERE (7) finished well back at Horsham last time when a 9 length seventh (27.74) but recorded best time of the card when winning four back. The form out of his last race has been franked. Has claims if he runs up to expectations. HECTOR DARCY (4) was safely held last time out, finishing eighth at this track over 525m behind Capricorn One (30.86) in a Grade 5. Scored at his previous run. Likely to be thereabouts. ZIPPING SINGH (8) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by half a length at this track in a handy 30.48 beating Rowdy Boy. Boasts two wins from four starts out of this box. Can measure up again. YAYA SALLY (1) can run a bold race on best form.",
